    <item>
      <title>迈阿密‘不可思议’的交通混乱表明南部经济繁荣的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-08-02/miami-real-estate-boom-leads-to-traffic-mess-for-politicians-and-billionaires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈阿密成为疫情爆发的城市后，交通拥堵问题急剧恶化，交通堵塞每年给该市造成 31 亿美元的损失。现在，政客和亿万富翁正在努力寻找解决方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-08-02/miami-real-estate-boom-leads-to-traffic-mess-for-politicians-and-billionaires</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 12:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银股价暴跌，孙正义财富蒸发 26 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-plunge-wipes-2-5-billion-off-masayoshi-son-s-fortune</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团股价连续两天暴跌，导致其创始人孙正义的财富缩水 26 亿美元，原因是这位科技投资者受到了日本央行比预期更早加息的冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-plunge-wipes-2-5-billion-off-masayoshi-son-s-fortune</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:53:28 GMT</pubDate>
